Sniper


Sniper relized he need to get to his cell. He walked to his cell 
having no one notice him. He placed the Rifle under his cot as well
as 
the nail. Then Sniper was about to lock his cell door when he looked 
at his window. for some reason it got bigger or something. Sniper 
calls out on his com, "Excuse me but I don't rememmber ordering a 
window job to my window. and whoever placed it in must of put a bomb 
in it or something cause it is all messy."
